{
  "texts": [
    "EvidenceInference is proposed without retrieval, so there is no prior model performance to report.",
    "Results for SciFact and ILDC are in Table 7 (Appendix).",
    "Macro F1 averages F1 scores across classes, while Micro F1 calculates F1 from aggregated results.",
    "and thus risk of hazards are typically low.",
    "These are tasks we recommend deprioritizing."
  ]
}